@startuml
!pragma teoz true
title Payment Sequence - Split Update Phase
hide footbox
participant Alice
participant Bob
participant Carol
participant Dave

== Update ==

Alice -> Bob: update_add_htlc(h_A)

Alice <-> Bob: commit
& Bob -> Carol: update_add_htlc(h_A)

Bob <-> Carol: commit
& Carol -> Dave: update_add_htlc(h_A)

Carol <-> Dave: commit

Dave -> Carol: ACK
& Carol -> Bob: ACK
& Bob -> Alice: ACK

Alice -> Dave: send r_A

== Settlement ==

Dave -> Carol: update_fulfill_htlc(r_A)
& Carol -> Bob: update_fulfill_htlc(r_A)
& Bob -> Alice: update_fulfill_htlc(r_A)

Dave <-> Carol: commit
& Carol <-> Bob: commit
& Bob <-> Alice: commit

@enduml
